
Ranger Help for: enemy horse
============================

SUMMARY:
Choosing horse means your Ranger specializes against horses, wild mounts,
mustangs, chargers, and similar equine creatures.

This is a plains, forest, hill, mountain, desert, and arctic choice. Keep
in mind that your follower will never be the same race as your enemy.

COMMAND:
  setenemy horse

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: enemy, setenemy and followers
